{"messages": [[{'role': 'user', 'content': "I'm thinking about designing a motel near an airport. What type should I consider?"}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': "You should consider designing an Airport Inn. It's built at major international airports and offers a large and high-class operation, which is ideal for travelers needing accommodation near an airport."}]]}
{"messages": [[{'role': 'user', 'content': 'My motel project is intended for vacationers looking for recreational activities. Any advice on what type of motel to choose?'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': "In this case, you should consider a Resort Motel. It's intended for guests already at their destination who require ample recreational facilities. Focus on amenities like pools, spas, and outdoor activities."}]]}
